label("$y$", (0, 15), N);

[/asy]

solution:
If point $T$ is placed at $(2,0)$, then $T$ is on $OB$ and $AT$ is perpendicular to $OB$. [asy]
size(5cm);defaultpen(fontsize(9));
pair o = (0, 0); pair q = (0, 12); pair b = (12, 0);
pair a = (2, 12); pair t = (2, 0);

draw((-2, 0)--(15, 0), Arrow);
